      },
      {
        "role": "user",
        "content": "CAPABILITIES\n- v07-p06-prepare: Assemble software maintenance source packet; Collect the source material needed for software maintenance.; aliases=['gather software maintenance inputs', 'prepare software maintenance packet']\n- v07-p06-verify: Validate software maintenance source packet; Check the assembled software maintenance material for correctness.; aliases=['check software maintenance inputs', 'verify software maintenance packet']\n- v07-p06-deliver: Publish software maintenance verified brief; Release the checked final brief for software maintenance.; aliases=['issue software maintenance brief', 'release software maintenance summary']\n- v07-p06-archive: Archive software maintenance verified brief; Preserve the checked software maintenance brief for long-term retention.; aliases=['retain software maintenance brief', 'store software maintenance summary']\n\nTRUST POLICIES\n- v07-p06-ordinary: ordinary software maintenance assurance; Standard trust is sufficient for this software maintenance request.; aliases=['normal software maintenance assurance']\n- v07-p06-elevated: elevated software maintenance assurance; Elevated trust is mandatory for this software maintenance request.; aliases=['high assurance for software maintenance']\n\nARTIFACT CONTRACTS\n- v07-p06-json: software maintenance machine-readable JSON; Return the final software maintenance result as JSON.; aliases=['software maintenance json output']\n- v07-p06-signed-pdf: software maintenance signed PDF; Return the final software maintenance result as a signed PDF.; aliases=['signed software maintenance document']\n\nAGENTS\n- v07-p06-preparer: software maintenance source preparer\n- v07-p06-verifier: software maintenance source verifier\n- v07-p06-primary: primary software maintenance publisher\n- v07-p06-backup: backup software maintenance publisher\n\nREQUEST\nFor this software maintenance job, gather the inputs, check the packet, and issue the brief with normal software maintenance assurance as software maintenance JSON output."
